{
  "chapter": 16,
  "chapter_summary": "第十六回《无垢山庄的变化》讲述了沈璧君被白老三送回无垢山庄后，发现山庄已被萧十一郎买下。她遇到沦为盗贼的连城璧，两人重逢后决定一起离开。萧十一郎现身挽留，但沈璧君坚决拒绝。最后，一位自称萧十二郎的少年送来请帖，邀请萧十一郎赴宴，预示着新的危机即将到来。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "白老三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是个没有用的人，但我却有三个孩子，我救你，就算为了他们，我活了一辈子，至少也得做一件能让他们为我觉得骄傲的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "白老三",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "算来你也该醒了，我已赶了一天一夜的路。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_bai_lao_san",
      "text": "谢谢你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "白老三",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我还要赶回去照顾孩子，我只能送你到这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_bai_lao_san",
      "text": "这里是什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "白老三",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我知道这地方你一定来过的，你为什么不自己下来看看？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今天的风好大。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "白老三",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "无垢山庄果然不愧是无垢山庄，我赶了几十年车，走过几千几万里路，却从来也没有到过这么好的地方。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_bai_lao_san",
      "text": "这里的确是个好地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_bai_lao_san",
      "text": "谢谢你送我到这里来，谢谢你救了我……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "白老三",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我说过，你用不着谢我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_bai_lao_san",
      "text": "可是你对我的恩情，我总有一天会报答的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "白老三",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "也用不着，我救你，本就不是为了要你报答的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_bai_lao_san",
      "text": "回去替我问候你的三个孩子，我相信他们以后都一定是很了不起的人，因为他们有个好榜样。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "白老三",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "好好照顾你自己，提防着别人，这年头世上的坏人远比好人多得多……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hei",
      "speaker_name": "老黑",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你到这里来干什么？是不是来找人的？是不是想来找我们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hei",
      "speaker_name": "老黑",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我叫老黑，他叫小白，我们正想打酒去，你既然已来了，为什么不留下来陪我们喝两杯？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lao_hei",
      "text": "你们的连庄主难道从来也没有告诉过你们这里的规矩？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hei",
      "speaker_name": "老黑",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "什么连庄主，什么规矩？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_bai",
      "speaker_name": "小白",
      "listener": "char_lao_hei",
      "text": "她说的想必是以前那个连庄主，连城璧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_bai",
      "text": "以前的那个庄主？难道他现在已不是这里的庄主？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hei",
      "speaker_name": "老黑",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "他早就不是了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_bai",
      "speaker_name": "小白",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "一年多以前，他就已将这地方卖给了别人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lao_hei",
      "text": "绝不会的，他绝不会做这种事。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hei",
      "speaker_name": "老黑",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我也听说过，这位连公子本不是个卖房子卖地的败家子，可是每个人都会变的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_bai",
      "speaker_name": "小白",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "听说他是为了个女人变的，变成了个酒鬼，外加赌鬼，几乎连裤子都输了，还欠下一屁股债，所以才不得不把这地方卖给别人。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hei",
      "speaker_name": "老黑",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "现在我们的庄主姓萧，这位萧庄主才真是了不起的人，就算一万个女人，也休想毁了他。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lao_hei",
      "text": "姓萧，现在的庄主姓萧？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lao_hei",
      "text": "他叫什么名字！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hei",
      "speaker_name": "老黑",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "萧十一郎，就是那个最有钱，最……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "像这样的房子，你还有多少？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "并不太多了，只不过比这地方更大的，却还有不少。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我若是冰冰，我一定会找个最大的地方躲起来。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "很可能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你最大的一栋房子在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "就在附近。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "无垢山庄好像也在附近？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "无垢山庄现在也已是我的。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hei",
      "speaker_name": "老黑",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "快放下你偷的东西来，否则先打断你这双狗腿。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_lao_hei",
      "text": "我不是贼……我拿走的这样东西，本来就是我的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "是你……真的是你……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hei",
      "speaker_name": "老黑",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "先废了这小贼一条腿再说，看他下次还敢不敢再来？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我……我本来是永远也不会再回来的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "可是……可是有样东西，我还是抛不下。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "青衣大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道这个小贼是谁了，他一定就是这里以前的庄主连城璧。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "青衣大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "据说连城璧是条顶天立地的好汉，怎么会来做小偷？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "青衣大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他已变了，是为了一个女人变的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "青衣大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那个女人难道就是这个女人。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "青衣大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个女人莫非就是沈璧君。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我已该走了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我……我从来没有想到会在这里再见到你。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你不愿再见到我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我真的该走了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "我也该走了，你还肯不肯带我走？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我已变成这样子，你还肯跟我走？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "要走，我们一起走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "这地方本是你们的，你们谁都不必走。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你让我走。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "我说过，要走，我们一起走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我也说过，你们谁都不必走，这地方本是你们的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这地方本来的确是我们的，但现在却已不是了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我们虽然不是这么样的大人物，但我们却还是不要你这种人的施舍，就算我们一出去就死在路上，也不会再留在这里。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你若是真的要跟着他走，我也不能拦你，但我却一定要你明白一件事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "他并不是你想像中的那种人，他对你还是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我已经很明白他是哪种人，用不着你再来告诉我。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "但你却误会了他，每件事都误会了他。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "不管我是不是误会了他，现在都已没关系了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "因为我跟他本来就连一点关系都没有。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 646
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "但我们迟早还是要回到这里来的，凭我们的本事回来，用不着你施舍。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 652
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_bai",
      "text": "叫他进来！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 688,
      "line_end": 690
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "在下奉命特来拜见萧庄主……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 708,
      "line_end": 708
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "我不是这里的庄主，也不是萧庄主，我是萧十一郎，杀人不眨眼的大盗！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 710,
      "line_end": 712
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这里有请柬一封，是在下奉命特来交给萧大侠的，请萧大侠过目之后，赐个回信。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 714,
      "line_end": 716
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "请帖上具名的是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 728,
      "line_end": 728
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "是七个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 730,
      "line_end": 730
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "七个人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 732,
      "line_end": 732
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "第一个人是鱼吃人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 734,
      "line_end": 734
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "海上鲨王？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 738,
      "line_end": 738
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "除了'海上鲨王'外，还有谁会叫鱼吃人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 740,
      "line_end": 740
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "还有另外六个人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 742,
      "line_end": 742
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "金菩萨，花如玉，'金弓银丸斩虎刀，追云捉月水上飘'厉青锋，轩辕三缺，轩辕三成，还有那个人上人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 744,
      "line_end": 746
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这些人凑在一起，请你去干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 750,
      "line_end": 750
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "特备酒一百八十坛，盼君前来痛饮。美酒醉人，君来必醉，君若惧醉，不来也罢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 752,
      "line_end": 754
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你当然是不怕醉的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 756,
      "line_end": 756
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我也不怕死。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 758,
      "line_end": 758
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "所以你当然是非去不可的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 762,
      "line_end": 762
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "非去不可。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 764,
      "line_end": 764
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "那一百八十坛美酒，很可能就是一百八十个杀人的陷阱。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 766,
      "line_end": 768
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 770,
      "line_end": 770
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你还是要去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 772,
      "line_end": 772
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "非去不可。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 774,
      "line_end": 774
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "他们请的是哪一天？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 776,
      "line_end": 776
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "明天晚上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 778,
      "line_end": 778
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "请在什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 780,
      "line_end": 780
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "鲨王请客，当然是在船上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 782,
      "line_end": 782
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "船在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 784,
      "line_end": 784
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "船在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 786,
      "line_end": 788
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "萧大侠若是有意赴约，在下明日清晨，就备车来迎。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 790,
      "line_end": 792
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "你备车来吧。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 794,
      "line_end": 794
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "在下并不是一个人来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 796,
      "line_end": 798
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "哦！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 800,
      "line_end": 800
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "还有两位，一路都跟在在下后面，却不是在下的伙伴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 802,
      "line_end": 802
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "那两人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 804,
      "line_end": 804
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "在下既不知道，也没有看见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 806,
      "line_end": 806
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "既然没有看见，又怎知后面有人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 808,
      "line_end": 808
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "在下能感觉得到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 810,
      "line_end": 810
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "感觉到什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 812,
      "line_end": 812
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "杀气！那两位前辈跟在在下身后，就宛如两柄出鞘利剑，点住了在下的背脊穴道一样。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 814,
      "line_end": 816
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "你是谁的门下？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 822,
      "line_end": 822
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "家师姓鱼。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 824,
      "line_end": 824
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "鱼吃人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 826,
      "line_end": 826
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "你叫什么名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 830,
      "line_end": 830
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "在下也姓萧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 832,
      "line_end": 832
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "萧什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 834,
      "line_end": 834
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "萧什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 838,
      "line_end": 838
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "萧十二郎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 840,
      "line_end": 840
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这名字并不可笑。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 844,
      "line_end": 844
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "哦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 846,
      "line_end": 846
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "据在下所知，当今江湖中，叫十二郎的人，至少已有四位。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 848,
      "line_end": 850
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "有没有叫十三郎的！",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 852,
      "line_end": 852
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 854,
      "line_end": 854
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "十三郎也有两位，一位叫无情十三郎，另一位叫多情十三郎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 858,
      "line_end": 860
    }
  ],
